anges. XRP is at a turning point as we approach the ETF results. ETF flows staying steady and general market sentiment improving could cause XRP to level off and start building a recovery base. Further downside pressure is still possible, though, if ledger activity keeps showing heavy distribution and ETF flows fall short of expectations.0:{"buildId":"nyNMduq-QDcIzXqHG9EwS","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","header",null,{"className":"site-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"header-inner","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/","className":"header-brand","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"header-logo","children":"C"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"header-text","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":["Cryptonews",["$","span",null,{"children":".in.th"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Crypto Intelligence Aggregator"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"header-status","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"status-dot"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Live Feed Active"}]]}]]}]}]}],["$","$L3",null,{"article":{"_id":"6985fd6a20f2cc25606bbc1e","guid":"https://u.today/200-xrp-ledger-growth-dynamic-precedes-major-etf-movement","slug":"200-xrp-ledger-growth-dynamic-precedes-major-etf-movement","title":"200% XRP Ledger Growth Dynamic Precedes Major ETF Movement","link":"https://u.today/200-xrp-ledger-growth-dynamic-precedes-major-etf-movement","pubDate":"2026-02-06T14:22:00.000Z","content":"XRP sees substantial growth on the Ledger, and it is not a good sign in absence of ETF data.","author":"Arman Shirinyan","enclosure":"https://u.today/sites/default/files/styles/twitterwithoutlogo/public/2026-02/100161.jpg","source":"U.Today","sourceCategory":"general","category":"altcoins","categories":["altcoins","regulation"],"summary":"","translatedTitle":"การเติบโตของ XRP Ledger 200% ก่อนการเคลื่อนไหวครั้งใหญ่ของ ETF","translatedContent":"XRP มีการเติบโตอย่างมากบน Ledger และนี่ไม่ใช่สัญญาณที่ดีในช่วงที่ยังไม่